description:
drh added on 2019-08-26 13:24:55:
The UPDATE statement in the following code fragment causes an assertion fault:
CREATE TABLE t1(a,b);
INSERT INTO t1 VALUES(1,2);
UPDATE t1 SET (a,a,a,b)=(SELECT 99,100);
This issue was discovered during internal testing.  There have been no reports
of problems in the wild.  Bisecting shows that the error was introduced by
check-in [36944be6be5c4209] on 2017-01-03 and first appeared in release
3.17.0.
